                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="talk_time">
            <div class="icon_float">
                <a href="/search?tid=151" title="人工智能"><img
                        width="64" height="64"
                        src="https://icon.solidot.org/images/topics/topicAI.png" alt="人工智能" /></a>
